{"tid":2340217,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本土派擬組議政平台　徐英偉譴責　稱非法理據充分、不容試探紅線","createTime":"2020-12-25T09:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T11:00:10.000Z","uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c6955e197613a63b236326456b9c1b8d4c360983","tid":2340217,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:30:03.000Z","msg":"民政事務局局長徐英偉接受訪問時被問到有區議員將宣布成立議政平台，他反問：「日日企圖以政治議題搞亂香港，究竟居心何在？」他續指，<span class=\"red\"><strong>平台非法的理據充分，他會密切關注</strong></span>，一旦越雷池半步，有關執法部門必定會採取行動，絕不容許任何試探紅線的舉動。<br />\n<br />\n他進一步以港被國安法舉例指，當中第六條列明所有公職人員都需要依法宣誓或簽署聲明擁護基本法，效忠香港特別行政區；第三十五條指，經法院判決危害國家安全罪行的人，將即時喪失參選資格。他續指，<strong><span class=\"red\">港府今後會在憲制秩序和政治體制上，正本清源、撥亂反正</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n徐英偉稱，過去一年香港經歷社會動盪，有部分別有用心的人煽動社會仇恨、搞亂香港秩序，在國安法落實後雖然表面上稍為平靜，但絕不能鬆懈，政府會嚴正執法，<strong><span class=\"red\">只要證據顯示任何人犯法，不論該人的身份和背景，都需要面對法律的制裁</span></strong>。他表明，政府未來將進一步加強市民的國安和守法意識。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 支那01<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/566276/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E6%B4%BE%E6%93%AC%E7%B5%84%E8%AD%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0-%E5%BE%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%81%89%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC-%E7%A8%B1%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%90%86%E6%93%9A%E5%85%85%E5%88%86-%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E8%A9%A6%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%85%E7%B7%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F566276%2F%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E6%2593%25AC%25E7%25B5%2584%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E5%25BE%2590%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%2585%2585%25E5%2588%2586-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E6%258E%25A2%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%25B7%259A&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQP56hpy2SSQtx6ElJ%2BvIbMI%3D&h=8040d5b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/566276/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%9F%E6%B4%BE%E6%93%AC%E7%B5%84%E8%AD%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0-%E5%BE%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%81%89%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC-%E7%A8%B1%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%90%86%E6%93%9A%E5%85%85%E5%88%86-%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E8%A9%A6%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%85%E7%B7%9A</a>"},{"pid":"c4d6230937a75a7dfa7ccdeae511a8c3bf923695","tid":2340217,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86282825fde809380ee4d8a15db725d38acd288a","tid":2340217,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T10:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed7bc08955a9cbc205680823f53be1f606db708","tid":2340217,"uid":117689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T10:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffd19eec0001a0faab5e4cbb755a00c49a93b49","tid":2340217,"uid":174607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ed7bc08955a9cbc205680823f53be1f606db708","tid":2340217,"uid":117689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T10:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T11:00:10.000Z","msg":"就係專登唔講明 等香港人個個自我審查"}]}